      <div class="max-w-[800px] text-foreground text-[16px] leading-[1.7] text-left" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sloumg">
        <h1 class="text-dark text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:ev5doi">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-16" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7mn">Last Updated: January 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-0" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sloumh">
          <section class="mt-12" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:xtpw2w">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:tjkaw8">1. Acceptance of Terms and Legal Capacity</h2>
            <p class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7mm">By accessing, browsing, or utilizing the SPVH Private Limited website, any of its affiliated verticals, or submitting information through our program intake forms (such as "The First Cheque"), you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be legally bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must immediately discontinue use of the platform.</p>
            
