              <strong class="block mb-2">Legal Capacity:</strong>
              You represent and warrant that you are at least 18 years of age and possess the legal authority to form a binding contract under the Indian Contract Act, 1872. If you are accessing this platform and submitting business data on behalf of a corporate entity, startup, or family enterprise, you warrant that you are an authorized representative with the power to bind that entity to these terms.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:electronic-record-p">
