            </p>

            <p class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:modifications-p">
              <strong class="block mb-2">Modifications to Terms:</strong>
              SPVH Private Limited reserves the sole right to update, amend, or replace these Terms of Service at any time without prior individual notice. It is your responsibility to check this page periodically for changes. Your continued use of the platform following the posting of any changes constitutes your binding acceptance of those modifications.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mt-12" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:xtpw2v">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:tjkaw8-2">2. Use of the Platform</h2>
            <p class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7ml">SPVH Private Limited grants you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, and revocable license to access and use the platform strictly for informational purposes, to explore our business verticals, and to submit formal applications for our investment initiatives.</p>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:permitted-submissions">
              <strong class="block mb-2">A. Permitted Submissions and Program Applications:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7mo">When submitting business plans, pitch decks, financial models, or personal data to SPVH via our forms, you warrant that all provided information is accurate, truthful, and owned by you or your authorized entity. You acknowledge that submitting an application does not create a fiduciary, advisory, or contractual relationship between you and SPVH. SPVH reviews numerous business models and may currently be evaluating, or may in the future independently develop or invest in, ventures that are similar or identical to your submission. The mere act of submitting a proposal through this platform does not constitute a binding Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) or an obligation for SPVH to provide funding.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:prohibited-activities">
              <strong class="block mb-2">B. Prohibited Activities:</strong>
              <p class="mb-3" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7mn">As a condition of your use of the platform, you strictly agree not to:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 mb-6">
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslefb">Use the platform for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable local, national, or international laws (including SEBI and RBI regulations).</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslefa">Attempt to reverse engineer, decompile, disassemble, or derive the source code of any software or structure constituting the platform.</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslef9">Use automated scripts, spiders, crawlers, or data-mining tools to scrape, copy, or extract proprietary data, executive profiles, or investment criteria from the website.</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslef8">Impersonate any person or entity, or falsely state or misrepresent your affiliation with a person, family enterprise, or corporate entity.</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslef7">Utilize the platform's contact forms or email addresses to transmit unauthorized advertising, promotional materials, or "spam."</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:system-security">
              <strong class="block mb-2">C. System Security and Integrity:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7mm">You are prohibited from violating or attempting to violate the security of the platform. This includes, without limitation, attempting to probe, scan, or test the vulnerability of our systems, breaching authentication measures, or introducing malicious code, viruses, or trojans intended to disrupt the platform or its connected institutional networks. SPVH reserves the right to investigate occurrences that may involve such violations and may involve, and cooperate with, law enforcement authorities in prosecuting users who are involved in such violations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:suspension-access">
              <strong class="block mb-2">D. Suspension of Access:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7ml">SPVH reserves the absolute right to terminate, suspend, or restrict your access to the platform or any program submission portals, without prior notice or liability, for any reason whatsoever, including without limitation if you breach these Terms of Service.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mt-12" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:xtpw2u">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:tjkaw6">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:spvh-ownership">
              <strong class="block mb-2">A. SPVH Ownership:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7mk">The SPVH Private Limited platform, including but not limited to its design, architecture, text, graphics, logos, brand names, software, data algorithms, and written literature, is the exclusive intellectual property of SPVH or its licensors and is protected by Indian and international copyright, trademark, and intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, create derivative works of, publicly display, or commercially exploit any content from this platform without our express, prior written consent.</p>
