          <section class="mt-12" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:xtpw2t">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:tjkaw5">4. User Submissions</h2>
            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:nature-submissions">
              <strong class="block mb-2">A. Nature of Submissions:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7lu">Through our platform, specifically within "The First Cheque" and other vertical intake forms, you may submit business plans, pitch decks, financial models, cap tables, and other related documentation (collectively, "Submissions") for investment evaluation.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:rep-warranties">
