              <p class="mb-3" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7lt">By uploading or providing any Submission, you represent and warrant that:</p>
              <ul class="list-none pl-6 space-y-3 mb-6">
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslef6">(i) you are the sole and exclusive owner of the Submission or have all necessary rights, licenses, and consents to share it;</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslef5">(ii) the Submission does not infringe, misappropriate, or violate a third party's patent, copyright, trademark, trade secret, or other intellectual property rights; and</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslef4">(iii) the Submission does not violate any applicable law or regulation.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:no-nda">
              <strong class="block mb-2">C. No Default Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) or Fiduciary Duty:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7ls">As an active investment holding company, SPVH Private Limited receives a high volume of Submissions and business concepts. You explicitly acknowledge and agree that the mere act of submitting materials through this website does NOT create a confidential, fiduciary, or advisory relationship between you and SPVH. Unless and until a formal, written Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) is mutually executed by authorized representatives of both parties, SPVH assumes no obligation of confidentiality regarding your Submission. We strongly advise against submitting trade secrets or highly sensitive proprietary code through our initial web forms.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:retention-review">
              <strong class="block mb-2">D. Retention and Internal Review:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7lr">You grant SPVH and its affiliates a non-exclusive, royalty-free, internal license to retain, review, reproduce, and analyze your Submission for the purpose of investment due diligence, market research, and regulatory record-keeping. SPVH reserves the right to reject any Submission at its sole discretion and is under no obligation to return submitted materials or provide detailed feedback regarding our investment decisions.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:platform-feedback">
              <strong class="block mb-2">E. Platform Feedback:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7lq">Any feedback, comments, or suggestions you may provide regarding the SPVH website or our digital operations (separate from your business pitch) is entirely voluntary. SPVH shall be free to use such feedback as we see fit and without any obligation or compensation to you.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mt-12" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:xtpw2s">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:tjkaw4">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:as-is-basis">
              <strong class="block mb-2">A. "As-Is" and "As-Available" Basis:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7lp">The SPVH Private Limited platform, including all ecosystem portals, program applications, and literature, is provided strictly on an "as-is" and "as-available" basis. To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, SPVH expressly disclaims all warranties of any kind, whether express, implied, or statutory, including but not limited to implied warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, non-infringement, and uninterrupted or error-free operation.</p>
