            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:informational-purposes">
              <strong class="block mb-2">B. Informational Purposes Only (No Financial Advice):</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7lo">The content provided on this platform is for general informational and corporate profiling purposes only. Nothing contained herein constitutes certified financial, legal, tax, or investment advice. SPVH is not liable for any independent financial, business, or investment decisions you make based on the information provided on this platform.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:exclusion-damages">
              <strong class="block mb-2">C. Exclusion of Indirect and Consequential Damages:</strong>
              <p class="mb-3" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:5me7ln">To the fullest extent permitted by Indian law, in no event shall SPVH Private Limited, its directors, officers, employees, affiliates, or agents be liable to you or any third party for any indirect, consequential, incidental, exemplary, punitive, or special damages. This includes, without limitation, damages for loss of profits, loss of revenue, loss of goodwill, loss of data, or business interruption arising out of or in connection with:</p>
