                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sslef2">(ii) the submission, review, rejection, or loss of any pitch deck or business proposal (including "The First Cheque" program);</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:ssleeg">(iii) any unauthorized access to or alteration of your transmissions or data; or</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:ssleef">(iv) any errors, omissions, or inaccuracies in the platform's content.</li>
