            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:no-guarantee-uptime">
              <strong class="block mb-2">B. No Guarantee of Uptime:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:dxgc8n">While we strive to maintain a highly secure and functional digital infrastructure, we do not warrant or guarantee that the platform will operate uninterrupted, be error-free, or remain continuously available. Access to the platform may be temporarily suspended due to system errors, server outages, or events beyond our reasonable control (Force Majeure).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:routine-maintenance">
              <strong class="block mb-2">C. Routine Maintenance:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:dxgc8m">From time to time, we may restrict access to certain parts of the platform, or the entire platform, to conduct routine maintenance, security updates, or deploy new features. We assume no liability for any delayed, lost, or incomplete program applications (including to "The First Cheque") resulting from such downtime.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:user-infrastructure">
              <strong class="block mb-2">D. User Responsibility for Infrastructure:</strong>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:dxgc8l">You are solely responsible for making all arrangements necessary for you to have access to the platform, including maintaining secure internet connections, updating your browser software, and ensuring your devices are protected against malware. SPVH shall not be responsible for any connectivity issues or data breaches occurring on your personal or corporate networks.</p>
            </div>
