                <strong class="block text-dark mb-1">A. Entire Agreement:</strong>
                <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:dxgc8r">These Terms of Service, together with our Privacy Policy and Regulatory Disclosures, constitute the sole and entire agreement between you and SPVH Private Limited regarding your use of the platform. They supersede all prior and contemporaneous understandings, agreements, representations, and warranties, both written and oral, regarding the platform and your submissions.</p>
              </div>
              <div data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sloumg">
                <strong class="block text-dark mb-1">B. Waiver and Severability:</strong>
                <p data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:dxgc8q">No waiver by SPVH of any term or condition set forth in these Terms shall be deemed a further or continuing waiver of such term or a waiver of any other term. Any failure of SPVH to assert a right or provision under these Terms shall not constitute a waiver of such right or provision.</p>
              </div>
              <div data-ps="src/pages/terms-of-service.astro:sloumh">
                <strong class="block text-dark mb-1">C. Contact Us:</strong>
